So let's count the advantages of this game:

1. Easy to operate and easy to use: As long as your fingers can flexibly slide up and down on the screen, you can run to your heart's content by avoiding all kinds of roadblocks.

However, if you want to play well, you must have good hand-brain cooperation, fast eyes and hands, and high concentration. Otherwise, faster and more speed and complex railway systems and roadblocks will always stop you.

2. Wide audience: Because the rules of the game are simple and the operation are not complicated, from dozens of years old to children to a few years old, they can become players of this game. And now almost everyone has a smart device, and this mobile game is suitable for all ages, so the player base is very large. It is a sharp tool for exercising reaction ability, finger flexibility and time.

3. Anytime and anywhere: As a stand-alone game, it is always available. Whether it is at night of insomnia, or during ress and work breaks, you can play for a while and spend the fragmented time. Once you don't want to play, you can quit at any time.

As a one-handed mobile game, it is also very random. On the crowded morning rush bus, on the subway, one hand is holding the handle, and the other hand can run for a while to set a new record, and get rid of the embarrassing situation that it is easy to fall when playing games.
